 所此指标成绩下降，只有 15 所成绩上升。 总体上，2022QS 世界大学排名共有"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-88a12cdb3e0f1863adced99146e5c35e_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/463988313"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5I6LpdPG3ZE6EAMaCDY1Mzg3OTgyINvS/oUGMDA4kgtALHIJNDYzOTg4MzEzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1623290961.8609662", "card_id": "Q_438735007", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 168}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有没有什么高质量的虐文 ？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "越虐越好！！！！！"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/438735007"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5I6LpdPG3ZE6EAMaCDU5Nzc0OTYwIInt6v8FMAY4oQRALXIJNDM4NzM1MDA3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1623290961.8612242", "card_id": "Q_463925066", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 401}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待中山大学 2021 年招生大类及分流专业？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-2890b21bd6caa261d7e584f5f899110d_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/463925066"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5I6LpdPG3ZE6EAMaCDY1MzczODQ0IPeg/YUGMCQ41w1ALnIJNDYzOTI1MDY2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1623290961.8616338", "card_id": "Q_463999051", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 45}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待约基奇当选 2020-21 NBA 常规赛 MVP ？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "NBA 官方宣布尼古拉 - 约基奇当选 2020-21 赛季常规赛 MVP，具体的投票情况也被曝光。 在全部 101 张选票当中，约基奇获得了其中 91 张第一选票，库里获得了 5 张，此外恩比德、字母哥、保罗和罗斯也多获得